would stop and I'd pull out of a can

00:58:18.750 --> 00:58:21.140
of soup and I'd read
everything on that soup can.

00:58:21.140 --> 00:58:23.530
Yes, then I'd do the beans and
then I'd move on down the -

00:58:23.530 --> 00:58:25.000
I just had to be reading,
if I wasn't thinking

00:58:25.000 --> 00:58:34.230
in words I didn't feel like I
belonged on the planet, you know?

00:58:34.230 --> 00:58:37.290
&gt;&gt; The transformative
power of humor,

