01:01:40.650 --> 01:01:41.950
&gt;&gt; Stephen Graham Jones: Yes.

01:01:41.950 --> 01:01:43.250 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Eric Gansworth: Yes, we did that.

01:01:43.250 --> 01:01:44.550
&gt;&gt; Linda LeGarde Grover:
Yes, I know.

01:01:44.550 --> 01:01:50.860 position:56%
So I write a lot about - my research
